sequenceDiagram
    participant RSS as RSS Feeds
    participant Local as Ollama<br/>(Local AI)
    participant Storage as Local<br/>Storage
    participant Cloud as Gemini<br/>(Cloud AI)
    participant Output as Published<br/>Briefs
    participant Tel as Telemetry<br/>System

    Note over RSS,Tel: Type III Compliance: Raw Data Never Leaves Local Infrastructure

    RSS->>Local: Raw Article Content<br/>(8000 chars)
    activate Local
    Local->>Tel: Log: Processing raw content locally
    Local->>Local: Generate Technical Summary
    Local->>Local: Generate Lay Explanation
    Local->>Local: Extract Metadata & Tags
    Local->>Storage: Store: raw_content_excerpt
    Local->>Tel: Log: Raw data stored locally
    deactivate Local

    Note over Storage: ❌ Raw content stays local

    Storage->>Cloud: Send: Summaries ONLY<br/>(No raw content)
    activate Cloud
    Cloud->>Tel: Log: Processing summaries only
    Cloud->>Cloud: Quality Assessment (QA)
    Cloud->>Cloud: Expert Analysis
    Cloud->>Cloud: Priority Scoring
    Cloud->>Cloud: Insight Generation
    Cloud->>Storage: Return: Scores & Insights
    Cloud->>Tel: Log: Cloud analysis complete
    deactivate Cloud

    Storage->>Output: Generate: Daily Briefs & Weekly Blogs
    Storage->>Tel: Log: Publication generated

    Note over Output: ✅ Only derived insights published

    Note over Tel: All operations logged for compliance audit
